        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs. 9-12. Sierracapnia mono. Male: 9. Zephyr Cove, Nevada. Genitalia, dorsal, epiproct and knob on tergum 7. 10. Zephyr Cove, Nevada. Genitalia, lateral, epiproct and knobs on tergum 9. 11. Slinkard Creek, California. Knob on tergum 7, anterior. 12. Clear Creek, Nevada. Tip of paraprocts and fusion plate showing tube, dorsal, terminal." ;
